        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 3: 'Not technologically inclined and unable to help, Rosetta is in the room lost in thought.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 1008,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'What\\'s on your mind?', 3: '10', 4: 'Tired?', 5: '11'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": 12,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'I was just thinking about how many Forest Guards were born here.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": 12,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Maybe...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'I may be labeled a sinner all the same, but I don\\'t carry the same weight as Diana and the others.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'I was modified because of other reasons. After I was reborn, I\\'ve been fighting ever since.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 14,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'After all this fighting, I may have gotten stronger. But I still can\\'t change my misfortune...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
        "ActionId": 1009,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '8'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 24,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'And when I met you and Alpha, I really thought that was the end.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 25,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'But I survived, and then I had to face Alpha again. Then this time, I thought it would just be a few minor skirmishes...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 26,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Who\\'d have thought? We\\'re now up against that Amberia in the legends.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 1010,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'It\\'s just a coincidence.', 3: '18', 4: 'Looks like we\\'re all unlucky.', 5: '18'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: '...Of course, I by no means think I\\'m special. I\\'m just used to it is all.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'But enough about me... If the problem can be really solved this time, the Forest Guards can finally rest at ease.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 1012,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Why?', 3: '20', 4: 'But we can\\'t tell anyone about Amberia. Can we?', 5: '21'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": 500,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: '...Bygones can finally be bygones. And we can bring an end to the nightmare known as Amberia.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": 500,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'It doesn\\'t matter. What matters is that we put the past to rest.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 500,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '4'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'In fact, many people in the ARU think that the \"tide\" is just a ruse by the Forest Guard to ensure our status.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'They\\'re always afraid that we will become the next Amberia.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'They\\'ve always been in fear, in fear that another Amberia will rise in the ARU.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 7001,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Fearing... even with that master code they programmed us with—the code to make us listen to their commands.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'However, not a single Forest Guard wishes to harm each other, because \"even amid torrential snow and wind, the Forest Guard\\'s honor stands strong.\"', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'This is an old saying among the Forest Guard... Well, I guess the Forest Guard aren\\'t exactly that old.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 1014,
        "NextActionId": null,
